Hidden One:

Grimlock looked at Slage. "Yes, something up, come Slag, we go see.
Sludge, stay here with Swoop and Snarl, keep an eye on Decepticons."
Grimlock began to move towards Pacifix.

(By the way, where is the denting metal.)
